WEBVTT

01:27.410 --> 01:31.880
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.150 --> 01:34.900
[Episode 2]

01:35.310 --> 01:36.229
Hello, Xia Yi?

01:36.680 --> 01:37.479
It's Yan Ling.

01:39.280 --> 01:40.140
Did you know...

01:40.560 --> 01:42.200
that Leilei had a tattoo?

01:43.509 --> 01:45.200
You... just found out?

01:45.640 --> 01:46.920
When did she get it?

01:48.200 --> 01:49.710
She was very afraid of pain.

01:49.710 --> 01:51.440
She was even afraid of needles.

01:51.759 --> 01:53.490
How could she ever get a tattoo?

01:53.920 --> 01:55.720
The first time we were intimate,

01:55.870 --> 01:56.840
I noticed it.

01:57.789 --> 01:58.840
Having a tattoo

01:58.840 --> 01:59.920
wasn't a big deal,

02:01.040 --> 02:02.700
but I still asked her about it.

02:03.920 --> 02:04.590
She said

02:05.000 --> 02:07.040
it was just a memento of her past.

02:07.510 --> 02:09.710
But I know everything about her past.

02:10.520 --> 02:12.120
Didn't you just find out

02:12.520 --> 02:13.720
that she had a tattoo?

02:14.840 --> 02:17.310
I thought this was her privacy.

02:18.520 --> 02:19.980
She didn't want us to know,

02:20.400 --> 02:21.930
and we should respect that.

02:24.240 --> 02:27.100
Just thinking about her
lying in that cold place...

02:32.910 --> 02:33.710
Today...

02:35.520 --> 02:37.320
they closed the case as suicide.

02:38.910 --> 02:40.310
Tomorrow morning at 9:30

02:41.000 --> 02:42.400
at Xiaguan Funeral Home.

02:43.910 --> 02:45.040
You'll come, right?

02:46.190 --> 02:46.680
Got it.

02:47.150 --> 02:48.610
I'll definitely be there.

02:55.940 --> 02:57.930
[Ms. Xu, Class 3 (Grade 4)]
[Refuse] [Answer]

02:59.240 --> 03:00.490
Hello, Ms. Xu.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.870
He stole my little turtle

03:02.870 --> 03:04.030
just to get back at me!

03:04.030 --> 03:05.050
I didn't!

03:05.120 --> 03:05.840
Enough!

03:06.470 --> 03:07.750
Last time you hit our Haoyang,

03:07.750 --> 03:08.710
I didn't say anything!

03:08.710 --> 03:10.390
Now you're stealing from us?

03:10.590 --> 03:12.720
You... You have such a vile character!

03:14.870 --> 03:15.870
Did you hit him?

03:17.030 --> 03:17.700
Why?

03:19.710 --> 03:21.360
He called me a big liar...

03:22.680 --> 03:25.340
and said I even lied about
my godmother's death.

03:28.470 --> 03:30.079
Then my son was right to hit him.

03:30.079 --> 03:31.140
W-What did you say?

03:31.400 --> 03:33.680
You're accusing my son, Yan Jiale,
of stealing

03:33.680 --> 03:34.280
and lying.

03:34.590 --> 03:36.650
Those are very serious accusations.

03:37.280 --> 03:38.240
He didn't lie.

03:40.190 --> 03:42.380
We did just lose...

03:44.079 --> 03:45.610
a very close family member.

03:48.910 --> 03:51.000
Don't think that just because I said
he deserved it,

03:51.000 --> 03:53.060
you actually had the right to hit him.

03:53.520 --> 03:54.980
Haven't I told you before,

03:55.400 --> 03:58.930
only incompetent people resort to violence
to solve problems?

03:59.560 --> 04:01.000
I won't play any games today.

04:01.000 --> 04:02.400
I'll do five more pages
of workbook exercises

04:02.400 --> 04:04.000
and write a self-criticism.

04:06.930 --> 04:07.660
Hello.

04:08.080 --> 04:09.150
I'd like to ask

04:09.280 --> 04:10.750
if a woman

04:10.960 --> 04:12.630
had an eye-design tattoo done

04:11.700 --> 04:15.940
[List of Tattoos Shop in Lihai City]

04:12.800 --> 04:14.310
at your shop.

04:14.680 --> 04:15.680
She was in her 30s.

04:16.490 --> 04:18.149
I've sent you the design.

04:19.480 --> 04:20.120
Nobody?

04:21.630 --> 04:22.260
Thank you.

04:25.320 --> 04:28.250
I've finished the workbook
and the self-criticism.

04:34.480 --> 04:36.510
Did Godmother do a lot of bad things?

04:37.700 --> 04:41.240
Is it true that she stole a lot of money
from others and couldn't pay it back,

04:41.240 --> 04:43.370
so she committed suicide out of guilt?

04:44.720 --> 04:45.720
Who told you that?

04:45.820 --> 04:47.350
It's all over the internet.

04:52.159 --> 04:53.360
I'm not quite sure...

04:54.390 --> 04:56.720
about the full story
of your godmother yet.

04:56.720 --> 04:58.050
When I know everything,

04:58.310 --> 04:59.770
I'll definitely tell you,

04:59.870 --> 05:00.270
okay?

05:02.280 --> 05:04.410
What if she really did some bad things?

05:17.750 --> 05:19.610
I'll go pick up her parents later.

05:19.680 --> 05:21.880
You can go directly to the funeral home.

05:21.930 --> 05:23.000
Isn't Jiale going?

05:24.510 --> 05:25.710
Did you even tell him?

05:26.270 --> 05:27.920
I'm afraid he'd be too heartbroken,

05:27.920 --> 05:29.050
so I didn't tell him.

05:29.510 --> 05:30.720
Better not let him go.

05:31.560 --> 05:31.950
Okay.

05:33.300 --> 05:34.100
See you later.

05:51.830 --> 05:52.560
Get up.

05:53.560 --> 05:54.890
Come to the living room.

05:59.800 --> 06:00.400
Come here.

06:05.720 --> 06:06.410
Yan Jiale,

06:07.310 --> 06:09.510
do you know what makes me the most angry?

06:10.680 --> 06:11.750
It's not that you took
your classmate's thing

06:11.750 --> 06:12.830
out of curiosity.

06:13.280 --> 06:16.010
It's that you've shattered the trust
I had in you!

06:17.120 --> 06:18.120
In a bit, you need to take the turtle

06:18.120 --> 06:20.280
back to school and return it
to your classmate.

06:20.280 --> 06:21.810
Apologize properly to him.

06:22.120 --> 06:23.650
Then go find Ms. Xu yourself

06:24.000 --> 06:25.330
and admit your mistake.

06:25.830 --> 06:28.310
When you come back tonight,
we'll have a serious talk.

06:28.310 --> 06:29.770
Aren't you coming with me?

06:30.040 --> 06:30.900
I'm busy today.

06:32.270 --> 06:33.680
You need to take responsibility

06:33.680 --> 06:34.940
for your own mistakes.

06:55.909 --> 06:56.800
Her parents

06:56.800 --> 06:58.920
seem to have aged so much overnight.

07:00.600 --> 07:01.600
And Xia Yi,

07:02.510 --> 07:03.640
he's quite pitiful.

07:04.450 --> 07:06.210
Be nicer to Jiale these days.

07:06.470 --> 07:08.470
Pay more attention to his feelings.

07:09.360 --> 07:10.480
After all, since childhood,

07:10.480 --> 07:12.280
he's spent more time with Leilei

07:12.600 --> 07:14.000
than with you, hasn't he?

07:14.120 --> 07:15.780
He's not a little kid anymore.

07:17.080 --> 07:20.560
He needs to learn to be reasonable
and to distinguish right from wrong.

07:20.560 --> 07:22.290
No one can protect him forever.

07:22.310 --> 07:23.570
He's only 10 years old.

07:24.950 --> 07:25.750
Not everyone is like you,

07:25.750 --> 07:27.810
with such strong mental resilience.

07:28.120 --> 07:29.480
If Leilei hadn't told me,

07:29.480 --> 07:31.190
I wouldn't even have known I had a son.

07:31.190 --> 07:34.920
I only found out after I asked you—
and he was already over a year old.

07:38.240 --> 07:38.950
Ms. Xu.

07:39.600 --> 07:40.730
Hello, Jiale's mom.

07:40.920 --> 07:42.270
Is Jiale feeling better?

07:42.270 --> 07:44.200
Jiale? What's wrong with him?

07:44.270 --> 07:45.600
Didn't you send me a message this morning

07:44.570 --> 07:46.360
[Ms. Xu, Class 3 (Grade 4)]

07:45.600 --> 07:46.560
saying he wasn't feeling well

07:46.560 --> 07:47.870
and asking for time off for him?

07:47.870 --> 07:48.680
No, I didn't.

07:49.120 --> 07:51.050
I didn't send you a WeChat message.

07:51.800 --> 07:52.930
Then where did he go?

07:52.950 --> 07:53.890
He didn't come to school today.

07:53.890 --> 07:55.240
He didn't come to school?

07:55.240 --> 07:57.180
I dropped him off at school this morning!

07:57.180 --> 07:58.780
Then, I-I'll hurry home and check.

07:58.780 --> 07:59.440
Okay, okay.

08:00.040 --> 08:01.770
Did you two have another fight?

08:05.240 --> 08:05.900
Is he there?

08:06.160 --> 08:07.430
He's not at Leilei's place.

08:07.430 --> 08:08.960
He's not at my place either.

08:09.240 --> 08:10.040
Jiale!

08:12.240 --> 08:12.970
I-I'm sorry.

08:13.800 --> 08:14.600
I-I'm sorry.

08:15.000 --> 08:15.830
E-Excuse me,

08:15.830 --> 08:16.310
have you...

08:16.310 --> 08:17.710
have you seen this child?

08:18.430 --> 08:19.740
Have you seen this boy?

08:24.630 --> 08:25.520
Zihao's mom,

08:25.620 --> 08:27.630
has Jiale contacted Zihao today?

08:28.670 --> 08:29.430
It's okay, it's okay.

08:29.430 --> 08:30.030
Thank you.

08:33.270 --> 08:34.030
Have something to eat.

08:34.030 --> 08:35.600
Could something have happened to Jiale?

08:35.600 --> 08:36.750
Nothing will happen to him!

08:36.750 --> 08:38.280
Don't think that way, okay?

08:38.840 --> 08:39.549
He's such a smart kid.

08:39.549 --> 08:41.409
Nothing will happen to him, okay?

08:42.150 --> 08:43.409
Have some water first.

08:43.669 --> 08:44.930
Here, have some water.

08:47.520 --> 08:48.380
Longhui River.

09:06.600 --> 09:07.790
How could you... How could you...

09:07.790 --> 09:09.320
How could you run away from home?

09:09.320 --> 09:10.510
I've told you before...

09:10.510 --> 09:11.910
you're never allowed to do this,
no matter what!

09:11.910 --> 09:12.670
That's enough. Enough!

09:12.670 --> 09:13.320
We found him, that's what matters!

09:13.320 --> 09:14.650
Why are you hitting him?

09:15.030 --> 09:17.440
And you, you nearly scared us to death,
you know that?

09:17.440 --> 09:18.440
Apologize right now.

09:18.440 --> 09:20.240
What's the point of apologizing to me?

09:20.240 --> 09:22.740
Stealing, lying, and skipping school—

09:22.910 --> 09:24.080
look at yourself now.

09:24.080 --> 09:25.200
What have you become?

09:25.200 --> 09:26.360
No matter what happens in the future,

09:26.360 --> 09:27.720
don't ever do this again, understand?

09:27.720 --> 09:30.000
You went to Godmother's funeral today,

09:30.000 --> 09:30.660
didn't you?

09:33.510 --> 09:36.040
You were wearing black clothes
this morning.

09:36.360 --> 09:38.360
Dad is also dressed all in black now.

09:38.430 --> 09:39.380
[With respect, Yan Ling]

09:39.400 --> 09:41.970
[Deeply mourning Ms. Jian Leilei]

09:43.790 --> 09:45.240
You both kept it from me!

09:45.790 --> 09:47.200
We kept it from you because...

09:47.200 --> 09:49.600
Because you think she was a bad person

09:49.600 --> 09:51.740
whose mistakes couldn't be forgiven!

09:52.100 --> 09:54.430
You didn't want me to see her
one last time!

09:55.270 --> 09:55.910
Yan Ling,

09:56.910 --> 09:57.870
I'll leave

09:58.630 --> 09:59.490
the rest to you.

10:01.840 --> 10:03.120
Don't worry, Uncle.

10:03.530 --> 10:04.390
You don't even

10:04.390 --> 10:05.970
care about what I think.

10:06.000 --> 10:07.490
It doesn't even matter.

10:08.110 --> 10:10.150
All you care about is
whether I did the right thing

10:10.150 --> 10:11.520
or made mistakes.

10:12.600 --> 10:13.840
So what if I lied,

10:13.880 --> 10:15.680
skipped class, or stole things?

10:15.870 --> 10:17.580
This is who I am now!

10:18.960 --> 10:20.020
Alright, alright.

10:20.960 --> 10:21.540
Alright.

10:26.960 --> 10:27.600
Be good.

10:30.960 --> 10:32.960
Get in the car with me. Let's go home.

10:33.910 --> 10:34.480
Yan Ling!

10:36.600 --> 10:38.400
Let him stay at my place tonight.

10:49.480 --> 10:51.810
Selling the house and car should be enough

10:52.600 --> 10:54.030
to cover most of the money

10:55.360 --> 10:56.720
Leilei embezzled.

10:57.320 --> 10:57.910
Okay.

10:58.910 --> 11:00.110
In our Jian family,

11:00.390 --> 11:01.630
for generations...

11:03.240 --> 11:05.200
no one has ever broken the law.

11:07.080 --> 11:09.210
We don't want to go back there anymore.

11:09.910 --> 11:11.310
It's too heartbreaking.

11:13.630 --> 11:16.220
If you can't bear to,
we can keep the baby.

11:16.750 --> 11:18.200
I've passed my probation period,

11:18.200 --> 11:19.720
and my salary will go up every year.

11:19.720 --> 11:22.020
Don't worry. Just focus on your studies.

11:28.270 --> 11:29.360
I'm here for you.

11:29.360 --> 11:30.790
You and I—one birth mother
and one godmother—

11:30.790 --> 11:31.750
are both so capable.

11:31.750 --> 11:33.480
I'm sure we can raise one child,

11:33.480 --> 11:34.160
right?

11:34.870 --> 11:36.470
Everything will get better.

11:36.630 --> 11:38.000
It'll all work out fine.

12:05.790 --> 12:06.630
Ms. Yan?

12:17.560 --> 12:18.490
Are you alright?

12:21.270 --> 12:21.990
I'm fine.

12:26.870 --> 12:28.530
Have you had too much to drink?

12:29.500 --> 12:30.900
How about I take you home?

12:35.000 --> 12:37.150
I'm fine. I'm doing well.

12:37.460 --> 12:38.660
Don't worry about me.

12:50.930 --> 12:52.510
[8th Anniversary Sale—Shop 'Til You Drop]

12:53.630 --> 12:55.030
I'm fine. I'm doing well.

12:58.380 --> 13:00.370
[8th Anniversary Sale—Shop 'Til You Drop]

13:25.100 --> 13:27.570
♪ It's like a dream ♪

13:28.300 --> 13:31.240
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

13:32.510 --> 13:33.940
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

13:34.220 --> 13:38.750
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

13:40.070 --> 13:46.550
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

13:47.530 --> 13:53.290
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

13:53.770 --> 13:58.410
♪ Do you know that I love you, miss you,
resent you, and long for you? ♪

13:58.720 --> 14:01.080
♪ My love will never change ♪

14:02.220 --> 14:05.910
♪ Have you ever thought about ♪

14:06.140 --> 14:08.990
♪ The vow we once made? ♪

14:09.640 --> 14:13.300
♪ Even if you're drawn to the daffodils ♪

14:13.710 --> 14:16.340
♪ Blooming by the water ♪

14:18.270 --> 14:20.470
I wanted to write my thesis properly...

14:21.000 --> 14:22.200
But I didn't know what was wrong with me.

14:22.200 --> 14:24.260
I just couldn't continue writing...

14:25.390 --> 14:27.410
But... But Feng said

14:27.430 --> 14:28.980
if I couldn't graduate,

14:29.150 --> 14:29.690
I...

14:29.840 --> 14:32.120
I'd be even more unworthy of his family.

14:32.390 --> 14:34.000
If I don't get my diploma,

14:34.550 --> 14:36.590
my dad will kill me.

14:37.030 --> 14:38.730
You can rewrite your thesis.

14:39.200 --> 14:40.800
When you're feeling better,

14:41.150 --> 14:42.350
I'll help you with it.

14:43.270 --> 14:44.930
You'll definitely graduate.

14:46.600 --> 14:47.310
Don't cry anymore.

14:47.310 --> 14:47.910
It's okay.

14:48.000 --> 14:49.860
Actually, it's good to cry it out.

14:51.520 --> 14:53.000
Your mother is getting food
at the cafeteria.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.600
She won't be back right away.

14:54.730 --> 14:56.860
If you want to cry, cry it out properly.

14:57.870 --> 14:58.440
Ms. Yan.

15:18.960 --> 15:20.690
Can you help me with something?

15:22.390 --> 15:23.200
What is it?

15:23.500 --> 15:25.450
Can you help me contact

15:25.910 --> 15:26.480
Li Changning's boyfriend,

15:26.480 --> 15:27.600
Xu Feng,

15:28.030 --> 15:29.230
through your school?

15:32.030 --> 15:34.050
Come on!

15:32.060 --> 15:33.660
[Lihai University
of Finance and Economics]

15:42.910 --> 15:43.640
Come on!

15:51.000 --> 15:53.550
Feng, you're amazing!

15:53.680 --> 15:54.600
Here, you must be tired.

15:54.600 --> 15:56.330
Here, have something to drink.

15:58.430 --> 16:00.960
Don't you know I don't drink
such sweet stuff?

16:02.200 --> 16:03.060
Pick one, then.

16:03.270 --> 16:04.530
They're all ice-cold.

16:09.530 --> 16:12.270
[Lihai University
of Finance and Economics]

16:15.000 --> 16:15.710
Xu Feng!

16:16.680 --> 16:17.500
Xu Feng!

16:20.840 --> 16:21.540
Ms. Wang!

16:22.840 --> 16:24.100
I don't know anything.

16:24.840 --> 16:26.720
I've already broken up with Li Changning.

16:26.720 --> 16:28.180
If I keep caring about her,

16:28.320 --> 16:30.180
my girlfriend will call me a jerk.

16:31.530 --> 16:32.870
After the incident,

16:32.900 --> 16:35.430
we also talked to Xu Feng
about the situation.

16:35.610 --> 16:38.330
It was indeed just a relationship dispute.

16:38.530 --> 16:39.790
We're all very sorry

16:40.390 --> 16:41.550
that this happened.

16:42.750 --> 16:45.010
You were already dating a new girlfriend

16:45.510 --> 16:47.700
while you were still
with Li Changning, right?

16:47.700 --> 16:48.960
What are you implying?

16:49.150 --> 16:50.700
Feng broke up with her ages ago.

16:50.700 --> 16:51.510
She's the shameless one

16:51.510 --> 16:53.120
who kept clinging to Feng. Right?

16:53.120 --> 16:53.910
Excuse me, miss,

16:53.910 --> 16:54.870
which department are you from?

16:54.870 --> 16:55.810
I'm not from your school,

16:55.810 --> 16:57.610
so you've got no control over me.

16:58.190 --> 17:00.050
I can see you're very much in love.

17:00.930 --> 17:03.390
Since you believe so deeply in
what you have,

17:03.600 --> 17:04.930
could you please tell me

17:05.730 --> 17:07.109
why you snuck into the hospital

17:07.109 --> 17:08.510
in the middle of the night

17:08.740 --> 17:09.869
to see Li Changning?

17:12.790 --> 17:13.609
I didn't.

17:15.849 --> 17:16.680
[Hospital—1st & 2nd Floor Corridor]

17:18.510 --> 17:21.130
[1-2F Corridor, Inpatient Ward]

17:34.340 --> 17:37.590
[1-2F Corridor, Inpatient Ward]

17:40.770 --> 17:41.970
It was you, wasn't it?

17:52.640 --> 17:53.970
Li Changning went crazy

17:54.640 --> 17:55.900
and was hospitalized.

17:56.310 --> 17:57.550
What other reason could there be
for my girlfriend

17:57.550 --> 17:59.150
to visit her in the hospital?

18:01.110 --> 18:03.040
Does this really need explaining?

18:04.640 --> 18:06.300
Because she's kind-hearted.

18:08.640 --> 18:09.040
Right?

18:27.300 --> 18:28.790
Li Changning was throwing her life away
for love

18:28.790 --> 18:29.950
and got herself into this state.

18:29.950 --> 18:31.280
It's not worth it at all.

18:31.590 --> 18:32.200
That boy is

18:32.270 --> 18:34.020
clearly just playing with those girls.

18:34.020 --> 18:36.200
But for her, it was a profound love.

18:36.590 --> 18:38.640
Of course, she'd be in pain
after losing it.

18:38.640 --> 18:40.070
No matter how profound the love,

18:40.070 --> 18:41.530
it's not worth destroying yourself.

18:41.530 --> 18:43.720
It only makes the other person
despise you more.

18:43.720 --> 18:44.200
Ms. Yan.

18:44.960 --> 18:46.270
The reason I asked for your help

18:46.270 --> 18:48.400
is not only because you're her teacher

18:48.480 --> 18:50.110
but also because you're both women.

18:50.110 --> 18:51.240
I thought you would understand her better

18:51.240 --> 18:52.150
and empathize with her,

18:52.150 --> 18:54.210
rather than criticize her like this.

18:56.010 --> 18:57.540
You're a privileged woman,

18:57.750 --> 18:59.240
but have you really looked at

18:59.240 --> 19:01.200
what Li Changning's life has been like?

19:01.200 --> 19:03.200
Her parents did send her to college!

19:05.000 --> 19:06.530
But you should be able to hear

19:06.530 --> 19:09.130
the reluctance and resentment
in their words.

19:09.790 --> 19:12.510
She was probably overlooked
from the moment she was born.

19:12.510 --> 19:13.680
And after her brother was born,

19:13.680 --> 19:15.350
she was pushed even further
into the background.

19:15.350 --> 19:16.200
Then...

19:17.070 --> 19:19.210
a boy appeared in her life.

19:19.430 --> 19:20.560
He said he loved her.

19:21.270 --> 19:22.480
He told her she was the most

19:22.480 --> 19:23.570
beautiful and important girl

19:23.570 --> 19:25.370
in the world to him.

19:28.070 --> 19:29.830
Do you know what that means

19:29.850 --> 19:30.980
to Li Changning?

19:33.110 --> 19:36.750
If anything, with her childhood trauma
and family misfortunes...

19:36.750 --> 19:40.080
shouldn't she have become
more independent and resilient?

19:41.560 --> 19:43.090
But she's only 20 years old.

19:44.960 --> 19:46.000
Even you, Ms. Yan,

19:46.920 --> 19:48.650
haven't you also been drinking

19:48.750 --> 19:50.550
and crying alone in a back alley?

19:52.160 --> 19:53.360
When you were her age,

19:53.890 --> 19:54.590
didn't you ever

19:54.590 --> 19:56.590
lose your mind and go crazy for love?

19:56.920 --> 19:58.980
You don't need to guess about my past.

19:59.160 --> 19:59.960
Rest assured,

20:00.680 --> 20:02.940
my role as her teacher isn't just a title.

20:03.030 --> 20:04.070
She is my student,

20:04.550 --> 20:06.950
and I'll take full responsibility for her.

20:07.550 --> 20:09.160
From now on, you don't need to
concern yourself

20:09.160 --> 20:10.630
with anything besides her treatment.

20:10.630 --> 20:11.000
I...

20:17.070 --> 20:18.670
When you were her age,

20:18.920 --> 20:19.480
didn't you ever

20:19.480 --> 20:21.480
lose your mind and go crazy for love?

20:24.680 --> 20:25.480
Don't! Stop!

20:25.700 --> 20:26.760
Alright, alright.

20:27.400 --> 20:28.070
Yan Ling!

20:38.750 --> 20:39.240
Hello?

20:42.720 --> 20:43.310
What?

20:43.750 --> 20:45.480
Back off. Back off.

20:45.880 --> 20:47.640
I'm crazy! I'm not leaving the hospital!

20:47.640 --> 20:49.580
What are you doing?

20:49.600 --> 20:51.720
-Changning, don't be impulsive!
-Back off! Back off!

20:51.720 --> 20:53.270
-She doesn't want me.
-If you make me leave the hospital today,

20:53.270 --> 20:54.720
I'll die right here, believe it or not!

20:54.720 --> 20:56.380
I'll die right in front of you!

20:57.680 --> 20:58.910
No! No!

20:59.190 --> 21:00.310
It's okay! It's okay!

21:00.310 --> 21:02.720
-Mrs. Li, it's fine!
-Shut up! Shut up!

21:02.830 --> 21:03.760
Get out!

21:03.830 --> 21:04.880
Get out!

21:06.000 --> 21:07.200
Don't hurt yourself.

21:07.450 --> 21:08.180
Listen to me.

21:09.200 --> 21:10.200
I understand you.

21:10.680 --> 21:13.400
It's not that you don't want to
leave the hospital.

21:13.400 --> 21:15.200
You just don't want to leave him.

21:15.640 --> 21:16.090
Right?

21:18.240 --> 21:20.970
If your mother takes you home
after discharge...

21:22.340 --> 21:24.740
you'll never have a chance
to see him again.

21:26.770 --> 21:27.570
Calm down.

21:29.400 --> 21:29.940
Look.

21:32.960 --> 21:34.180
You're an adult now.

21:34.270 --> 21:36.180
If you just sign this form,

21:36.920 --> 21:37.580
your mother

21:37.720 --> 21:39.580
can't make any decisions for you.

21:40.920 --> 21:42.030
I don't believe you.

21:42.030 --> 21:43.480
I don't believe you! Take it away!

21:43.480 --> 21:45.550
Whether you leave the hospital or not
doesn't matter to me.

21:45.550 --> 21:46.160
Trust me.

21:46.510 --> 21:48.040
Just read it and you'll see.

21:49.370 --> 21:50.790
[Test Request Form]

21:56.480 --> 21:57.550
Even Ms. Yan

21:57.720 --> 21:58.520
and the school

21:58.960 --> 21:59.790
cannot

21:59.790 --> 22:01.920
make any discharge decisions for you.

22:03.480 --> 22:05.010
You'll know once you see it.

22:10.960 --> 22:13.140
Whether to leave the hospital or not...

22:13.140 --> 22:14.540
it'll be your own choice.

22:27.720 --> 22:28.550
Grab her. Grab her.

22:28.550 --> 22:31.190
You lied to me! You all lied to me!

22:31.230 --> 22:31.920
Why?

22:31.920 --> 22:33.070
Changning, calm down.

22:33.070 --> 22:33.660
Gently, gently.

22:33.660 --> 22:34.410
Be gentle.

22:35.480 --> 22:36.880
It's alright. It's alright.

22:36.880 --> 22:38.340
Changning, it's alright.

22:41.310 --> 22:42.910
It's alright. It's alright.

22:43.600 --> 22:44.840
Prepare the bed. Come on.

22:44.840 --> 22:45.640
It's fine now.

22:47.440 --> 22:48.270
Ms. Yan.

22:49.550 --> 22:50.890
Please tell me

22:51.270 --> 22:53.370
which boy it is.

22:53.480 --> 22:55.510
I'll beg him to leave my daughter alone.

22:55.510 --> 22:56.030
Ms. Yan.

22:56.680 --> 22:57.410
Thank you.

23:05.000 --> 23:05.810
Ma'am.

23:06.830 --> 23:08.690
You've been here for so many days.

23:09.270 --> 23:11.730
Has that boy ever come to
visit Li Changning?

23:12.640 --> 23:13.400
Do you think

23:14.200 --> 23:16.840
the one who won't let go
is him or Changning?

23:20.920 --> 23:22.450
Could you please promise me

23:23.510 --> 23:24.400
that you'll stop reminding her

23:24.400 --> 23:26.440
how much money the family spent on her,

23:26.440 --> 23:28.590
or that she has a brother to worry about?

23:28.590 --> 23:30.110
Just treat her

23:30.110 --> 23:31.770
as if she were your only child.

23:32.590 --> 23:34.650
Care about whether she's eating well

23:34.720 --> 23:35.720
or sleeping well.

23:36.550 --> 23:38.550
Even if it's just for these few days.

23:41.790 --> 23:42.830
But this child...

23:42.830 --> 23:44.400
You saw what she's like.

23:44.510 --> 23:45.970
Now, she's basically like

23:46.310 --> 23:48.910
someone who's taken a bad fall
and gotten hurt.

23:49.480 --> 23:50.920
Let's not blame her

23:50.920 --> 23:52.440
for not watching her step.

23:53.270 --> 23:54.410
Actually, she

23:54.830 --> 23:57.030
didn't want to fall and get hurt either,

23:57.310 --> 23:57.880
did she?

24:01.000 --> 24:01.620
Ma'am,

24:02.270 --> 24:04.130
please give me a little more time,

24:05.200 --> 24:07.530
and give Changning a little more time too.

24:09.310 --> 24:09.770
Then...

24:10.310 --> 24:12.400
that paper you just showed her—

24:12.400 --> 24:14.460
you absolutely can't let her sign it.

24:14.790 --> 24:16.270
She's too young and inexperienced.

24:16.270 --> 24:17.310
You mean this?

24:17.400 --> 24:17.870
Yes.

24:19.240 --> 24:20.110
This is fake.

24:20.110 --> 24:21.270
I was just tricking her.

24:21.270 --> 24:22.530
There's no such thing.

24:29.120 --> 24:32.270
Good thing you were here
when that patient lost control today.

24:32.270 --> 24:33.400
What's really going on with her?

24:33.400 --> 24:35.240
She's been here for days
and hasn't gotten any better.

24:35.240 --> 24:37.530
Just be patient
and treat the symptoms accordingly.

24:37.530 --> 24:38.390
Dr. Luo?

24:39.410 --> 24:40.060
Ms. Yan?

24:41.110 --> 24:41.960
I'll be going now.

24:41.960 --> 24:42.490
Bye-bye.

24:43.720 --> 24:45.180
You're... waiting for me?

24:45.790 --> 24:46.560
Dr. Luo.

24:47.240 --> 24:49.030
I'm really glad you were here today.

24:49.030 --> 24:49.720
Otherwise,

24:49.750 --> 24:51.750
who knows what might have happened?

24:51.880 --> 24:52.940
No need to thank me.

24:53.270 --> 24:54.520
About last time,

24:55.200 --> 24:57.070
I couldn't control my emotions.

24:57.720 --> 24:59.320
I wanted to apologize to you.

25:00.920 --> 25:01.640
Last time?

25:02.200 --> 25:04.260
Yesterday, after we met with Xu Feng.

25:06.880 --> 25:07.940
I was just kidding.

25:08.020 --> 25:09.280
Actually, I remember.

25:09.790 --> 25:11.850
I suddenly lost composure yesterday

25:11.960 --> 25:13.860
because, indeed, you'd seen me

25:14.350 --> 25:16.040
in such a terrible state

25:16.550 --> 25:17.420
that night.

25:18.000 --> 25:20.000
And then, hearing you mention it...

25:20.650 --> 25:22.270
I felt quite embarrassed.

25:23.070 --> 25:24.840
Actually, you don't need to
be embarrassed.

25:24.840 --> 25:26.640
Sometimes losing control is...

25:28.110 --> 25:29.570
a good defense mechanism.

25:29.590 --> 25:30.550
Being able to lose control means

25:30.550 --> 25:32.550
you feel safe in your surroundings.

25:32.590 --> 25:33.920
From that perspective,

25:35.070 --> 25:35.910
I'm honored

25:36.230 --> 25:37.630
that I make you feel safe.

25:41.590 --> 25:42.370
Dr. Luo,

25:42.830 --> 25:45.630
my son and I have been having
some problems lately.

25:46.160 --> 25:47.890
I'd like to ask for your advice.

25:49.000 --> 25:49.660
No problem.

26:13.300 --> 26:15.830
What kind of small animal
are you looking for?

26:15.880 --> 26:16.610
Just browsing.

26:16.230 --> 26:18.480
[Cute Pets Club]

26:17.000 --> 26:17.370
Okay.

26:23.240 --> 26:24.960
This one is a new arrival.

26:24.960 --> 26:26.000
It's called the Snowball Hamster.

26:26.000 --> 26:26.960
Very rare.

26:28.160 --> 26:29.590
Can you take it out
so I can see it better?

26:29.590 --> 26:31.190
It's actually quite fierce.

26:34.800 --> 26:36.130
I'll take this one then.

26:36.400 --> 26:37.880
I like ones with character.

26:37.880 --> 26:38.410
Alright.

27:05.340 --> 27:06.400
What are you doing?

27:07.830 --> 27:09.030
Getting some snacks.

27:10.310 --> 27:11.640
Perfect timing, Jiale!

27:12.000 --> 27:12.880
Come here. Stop doing homework.

27:12.880 --> 27:14.000
Watch the movie with us.

27:14.000 --> 27:15.060
This is super good.

27:15.850 --> 27:18.380
Kids will have nightmares
if they watch this.

27:18.400 --> 27:19.460
You want some cola?

27:20.000 --> 27:20.900
I'll just drink half of it.

27:20.900 --> 27:21.920
If you like it, drink it all.

27:21.920 --> 27:23.240
I'll buy you more tomorrow.

27:23.240 --> 27:25.700
Drinking too much of it
is bad for your teeth.

27:26.230 --> 27:28.360
Is that something a kid would say?

27:28.510 --> 27:30.680
You're even more old-fashioned
than your dad...

27:30.680 --> 27:33.010
even more mature and steady than your dad.

27:33.750 --> 27:34.830
I'm going back to do my homework.

27:34.830 --> 27:35.720
Still doing homework?

27:35.720 --> 27:37.830
You've been at it for two hours
and are still not finished?

27:37.830 --> 27:39.360
The school is way too crazy.

27:39.590 --> 27:40.390
That's not it.

27:40.440 --> 27:42.440
His mom has assigned him workbooks.

27:42.510 --> 27:43.000
Coming.

27:45.360 --> 27:46.000
I'm sorry.

27:46.000 --> 27:47.590
I didn't tell you in advance.

27:47.590 --> 27:48.490
Jiale.

27:49.110 --> 27:50.970
I wanted to give Jiale a surprise.

27:51.030 --> 27:51.680
Um...

27:54.400 --> 27:55.200
Is this a bad time?

27:55.200 --> 27:56.030
No, no, not at all.

27:56.030 --> 27:58.060
Well, l-let me introduce you...

27:59.590 --> 28:01.440
Hello, I'm Lu's girlfriend.

28:01.440 --> 28:02.570
My name is Fang Fang.

28:03.720 --> 28:04.510
Nice to meet you.

28:04.510 --> 28:05.710
I'm Jiale's mother.

28:06.350 --> 28:06.920
I know.

28:06.980 --> 28:08.480
Jiale was just talking about you.

28:08.480 --> 28:08.910
Right?

28:08.960 --> 28:09.690
No, I wasn't!

28:09.880 --> 28:10.940
Don't be like that.

28:11.270 --> 28:12.310
Well, look at you.

28:12.310 --> 28:13.310
I asked you to grab me a cola.

28:13.310 --> 28:14.370
It took you so long.

28:14.550 --> 28:15.310
This... I...

28:15.440 --> 28:15.920
I want to drink it.

28:15.920 --> 28:16.720
It's fine.

28:17.590 --> 28:19.440
Actually, having a few sips
of cola occasionally

28:19.440 --> 28:20.240
is no big deal.

28:23.920 --> 28:24.660
Jiale,

28:25.480 --> 28:26.740
come home with Mom.

28:27.790 --> 28:28.600
Why go home?

28:29.830 --> 28:31.960
It's not convenient for you
to stay here all the time.

28:31.960 --> 28:33.290
It's quite convenient.

28:33.590 --> 28:34.920
And I have someone to play with.

28:34.920 --> 28:37.050
Alright, alright, I'll play with you.

28:44.440 --> 28:45.940
Come home with me.

28:46.350 --> 28:48.350
I want to have a good talk with you.

28:49.070 --> 28:50.670
Why should I go home with you?

28:50.850 --> 28:52.380
You just want to lecture me!

28:52.480 --> 28:53.550
Have a talk with me?

28:53.550 --> 28:55.150
I don't want to talk with you!

28:55.680 --> 28:57.050
That's not what I meant.

28:57.160 --> 28:57.780
Jiale!

28:58.420 --> 29:00.590
I just want to have
a proper talk with you, Jiale!

29:00.590 --> 29:01.310
Yan Jiale,

29:01.310 --> 29:02.970
what kind of attitude is that?

29:04.510 --> 29:06.470
Kids are just like that.

29:06.590 --> 29:08.160
W-Why don't you come in
and sit for a while?

29:08.160 --> 29:09.560
Wait until he calms down.

29:10.640 --> 29:12.480
How about we let him cool off first

29:12.480 --> 29:14.010
and talk about it tomorrow?

29:18.720 --> 29:19.830
I'll be going then.

29:20.270 --> 29:20.820
Okay.

29:23.310 --> 29:24.070
Don't worry.

29:24.070 --> 29:25.070
He's fine with me.

29:35.720 --> 29:36.680
I told my colleagues

29:36.680 --> 29:38.200
that my son is already in fourth grade,

29:38.200 --> 29:38.830
and they thought

29:38.830 --> 29:41.350
I was lying just to get employee benefits.

29:41.550 --> 29:42.830
So we can really go see

29:42.830 --> 29:44.430
the premiere of Spider-Man?

29:44.960 --> 29:45.910
Of course.

29:46.000 --> 29:47.960
I even got you two

29:47.960 --> 29:49.030
autographed posters.

29:49.030 --> 29:49.720
Jiale,

29:49.960 --> 29:51.030
when I get married,

29:51.030 --> 29:52.030
you'll be my flower boy,

29:52.030 --> 29:52.770
okay?

29:53.270 --> 29:54.900
Godmother, you're the best!

29:56.160 --> 29:58.670
You're my guardian angel.

30:07.440 --> 30:08.240
You don't even

30:08.240 --> 30:09.900
care about what I think.

30:09.960 --> 30:11.370
It doesn't even matter.

30:11.960 --> 30:12.720
All you care about is

30:12.720 --> 30:14.000
whether I did the right thing

30:14.000 --> 30:15.300
or made mistakes.

30:15.550 --> 30:17.080
You just want to lecture me!

30:17.110 --> 30:18.710
I don't want to talk with you!

30:39.180 --> 30:41.830
[Dr. Luo Liang]

30:40.720 --> 30:41.530
How did it go?

30:41.680 --> 30:43.480
Did your talk with Jiale go well?

30:47.640 --> 30:49.100
Not as well as I expected.

30:54.240 --> 30:55.400
Patience is key.

30:59.260 --> 31:00.130
Okay.

31:05.000 --> 31:06.100
[How did it go?
Did your talk with Jiale go well?]

31:06.120 --> 31:07.270
[Not as well as I expected.]

31:07.290 --> 31:08.280
[Patience is key.]

31:08.310 --> 31:09.530
[Okay.]

31:20.400 --> 31:22.000
They say when a child is sick,

31:22.070 --> 31:24.470
they turn to the person
they're closest to.

31:25.160 --> 31:26.640
When Jiale was sick before,

31:26.640 --> 31:28.240
he always looked for Leilei.

31:28.350 --> 31:29.550
He never came to me.

31:32.070 --> 31:33.470
Today, it suddenly hit me

31:34.830 --> 31:36.700
that I'm not really a good mother.

31:44.790 --> 31:47.000
[Typing...]

31:55.250 --> 31:58.980
[Integrity in Character,
Diligence in Study]

31:55.550 --> 31:57.640
Now, the cause and course
of Li Changning's current condition

31:57.640 --> 31:58.720
are very clear.

31:59.280 --> 32:01.620
It was entirely due to emotional issues.

32:02.120 --> 32:03.760
Her frequent absences,

32:04.030 --> 32:05.200
late assignment submissions,

32:05.200 --> 32:07.520
and thesis plagiarism are all confirmed.

32:07.520 --> 32:10.110
Ms. Yan's decision to bar her
from the thesis defense

32:10.110 --> 32:13.160
was entirely in accordance with
regulations and procedures.

32:13.160 --> 32:14.890
There's nothing wrong with it.

32:15.310 --> 32:17.710
This matter has caused
quite a public stir.

32:18.070 --> 32:19.920
Since the matter has been
thoroughly investigated,

32:19.920 --> 32:22.720
we should issue an official statement
as soon as possible

32:22.720 --> 32:24.790
to address public opinion.

32:26.270 --> 32:28.870
We will be completely honest
in our statement.

32:29.200 --> 32:30.590
Regardless of which media outlets
contact us,

32:30.590 --> 32:31.350
we can

32:31.350 --> 32:32.470
clearly

32:32.470 --> 32:34.590
present the facts
and explain the whole thing.

32:34.590 --> 32:35.070
Good.

32:35.720 --> 32:36.370
Once it's finished,

32:36.370 --> 32:37.640
submit it to
the Administrative Office promptly.

32:37.640 --> 32:38.170
Alright.

32:39.550 --> 32:40.410
President Sun,

32:41.200 --> 32:42.730
I have a different opinion.

32:47.400 --> 32:48.310
This child...

32:48.880 --> 32:50.590
Her emotions have been
very unstable lately.

32:50.590 --> 32:53.990
A few days ago, she almost hurt
herself again in the hospital.

32:54.200 --> 32:55.530
She's only 21 years old.

32:56.350 --> 32:57.960
If she has to live the rest of her life

32:57.960 --> 33:00.220
under the stigma of plagiarism,

33:00.680 --> 33:03.030
and if we also disclose
that she had a breakdown

33:03.030 --> 33:04.760
due to relationship problems,

33:05.070 --> 33:06.430
it would be devastating

33:07.240 --> 33:08.720
for someone so young.

33:09.070 --> 33:10.400
That would be too cruel.

33:11.160 --> 33:11.960
Then, Ms. Yan,

33:12.510 --> 33:14.640
how do you think we should handle this?

33:14.640 --> 33:16.300
How about in the statement...

33:17.750 --> 33:19.150
we say that it was my fault

33:19.590 --> 33:20.230
for

33:20.550 --> 33:22.750
not supervising the student properly?

33:25.680 --> 33:26.250
Ms. Yan,

33:26.550 --> 33:28.010
you want to take the blame?

33:28.400 --> 33:29.200
Yes, Ms. Yan.

33:29.710 --> 33:34.150
[Integrity in Character,
Diligence in Study]

33:30.000 --> 33:31.070
If the statement is
really written that way,

33:31.070 --> 33:32.670
the school will have to

33:32.920 --> 33:34.680
take disciplinary action against you.

33:34.680 --> 33:36.480
That will seriously affect you.

33:36.480 --> 33:37.000
By then, this matter

33:37.000 --> 33:39.000
won't be something
that can simply be brushed aside.

33:39.000 --> 33:40.160
I'm her teacher.

33:42.270 --> 33:43.290
No matter what,

33:44.240 --> 33:45.440
I'm older than she is.

33:45.620 --> 33:46.850
[Integrity in Character,
Diligence in Study]

33:47.250 --> 33:48.490
How about this?

33:49.240 --> 33:49.890
Lin,

33:50.270 --> 33:51.150
be careful with

33:51.240 --> 33:53.150
how you word the statement.

33:53.800 --> 33:57.060
[Integrity in Character,
Diligence in Study]

33:53.930 --> 33:56.000
Don't publish it on the school website.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.260
Just post it on campus.

33:57.510 --> 33:59.710
Keep the impact as minimal as possible.

33:59.830 --> 34:00.360
Alright.

34:03.440 --> 34:05.710
-Actually, Ms. Yan is quite kind.
-We must handle it well.

34:05.710 --> 34:06.900
Keep the impact to a minimum.

34:06.900 --> 34:09.030
Alright, don't worry, President Sun.

34:16.840 --> 34:17.370
Let's go.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.030
Let's go to the cafeteria together.

34:19.030 --> 34:19.699
My treat.

34:20.000 --> 34:21.330
I packed my lunch today.

34:35.670 --> 34:38.110
Telling a mother who misses her son
to be patient

34:38.110 --> 34:41.040
is obviously
a completely meaningless suggestion.

34:41.190 --> 34:42.719
If you trust me and allow it,

34:43.070 --> 34:45.330
perhaps I could have a chat with your son.

34:57.230 --> 34:57.840
Goodbye.

34:59.350 --> 34:59.930
Jiale.

35:09.640 --> 35:10.150
Come on.

35:15.030 --> 35:17.540
I'm not here to force you
to come home with me.

35:18.190 --> 35:20.000
Your dad is working overtime today.

35:20.000 --> 35:23.000
He asked me to take you
to my office to do your homework.

35:23.090 --> 35:24.310
I'll take you to his place later,

35:24.310 --> 35:24.800
okay?

35:28.360 --> 35:29.090
Here, let me.

35:42.540 --> 35:43.090
[Bulletin Board]

35:43.110 --> 35:45.560
[Notice on the Sudden Incident]

35:45.590 --> 35:46.890
[Involving Li, Class of 2015]

35:49.130 --> 35:50.720
[Homeroom Teacher Yan Ling is responsible
for the Level-2 teaching incident]

35:50.740 --> 35:52.560
[due to improper handling.]

35:55.970 --> 35:59.840
[Bulletin Board]

36:08.560 --> 36:09.260
Come in.

36:11.230 --> 36:11.790
Hello.

36:13.070 --> 36:14.930
I'm looking for Yan Ling, Ms. Yan.

36:15.300 --> 36:17.110
She went to tutor a student
on their thesis.

36:17.110 --> 36:18.240
She'll be back soon.

36:19.920 --> 36:20.610
Then...

36:21.360 --> 36:22.620
I'll wait for her here.

36:26.630 --> 36:28.920
You can grab a chair and have a seat.

36:29.590 --> 36:31.320
It's fine. I'll stand for a bit.

36:35.320 --> 36:36.600
May I ask

36:37.000 --> 36:37.800
who you are?

36:38.590 --> 36:39.630
I'm her son.

36:39.730 --> 36:40.860
My name is Yan Jiale.

36:42.320 --> 36:42.840
Hello.

36:43.590 --> 36:44.520
Nice to meet you.

36:45.150 --> 36:46.200
My name is Luo Liang.

36:46.200 --> 36:49.400
I'm the attending physician
for one of her sick students.

36:49.590 --> 36:50.680
Is her illness

36:50.800 --> 36:52.480
really my mom's fault?

36:55.880 --> 36:58.540
That involves
the patient's personal privacy.

36:58.550 --> 36:59.810
I can't disclose that.

36:59.990 --> 37:01.590
But I can assure you

37:02.000 --> 37:04.320
that your mom is an excellent teacher.

37:05.550 --> 37:07.550
If she's really such a good teacher,

37:07.590 --> 37:09.320
why would she be disciplined?

37:12.800 --> 37:13.760
So, how do you

37:14.240 --> 37:16.330
and your father

37:16.590 --> 37:17.670
see your mom?

37:18.560 --> 37:20.620
How my dad sees my mom doesn't matter.

37:21.110 --> 37:22.710
He already has a girlfriend.

37:26.100 --> 37:26.960
What about you?

37:27.320 --> 37:28.920
What do you think of your mom?

37:42.480 --> 37:43.920
Thank you, Dr. Luo.

37:45.590 --> 37:47.390
There's nothing to thank me for.

37:47.440 --> 37:49.000
I made a new friend today.

37:49.510 --> 37:51.110
It was great meeting you too.

37:51.970 --> 37:52.920
I've got some things at the hospital.

37:52.920 --> 37:53.920
I'll be going now.

37:54.710 --> 37:55.710
Bye-bye, Dr. Luo.

37:55.840 --> 37:56.370
Bye-bye.

37:57.150 --> 37:57.900
You two...

37:58.440 --> 37:59.700
take your time to talk.

38:06.070 --> 38:07.760
I'll take you to your father's place.

38:07.760 --> 38:08.620
Are you hungry?

38:08.840 --> 38:10.770
Do you want to eat something first?

38:12.480 --> 38:13.770
I want to go home.

38:19.710 --> 38:22.190
I mean, I want to go back to my own home.

38:33.550 --> 38:34.880
When did you learn this?

38:35.000 --> 38:35.860
Who taught you?

38:36.670 --> 38:37.880
My godmother taught me.

38:37.880 --> 38:40.110
So you and your godmother were very close.

38:40.110 --> 38:40.790
Yes.

38:43.150 --> 38:45.950
You said your godmother was gentler
than your mom.

38:46.920 --> 38:49.360
So, is this a drawing of you
and your godmother?

38:49.360 --> 38:51.020
I miss my godmother very much.

38:55.560 --> 38:56.680
Dealing with loss

38:57.230 --> 38:58.710
is a very difficult thing.

38:59.960 --> 39:02.960
Stealing a turtle, lying,
and running away from home—

39:03.440 --> 39:06.170
those things might seem serious
at first glance,

39:06.190 --> 39:07.000
but in truth,

39:07.000 --> 39:09.520
they're just Jiale's stress responses

39:09.590 --> 39:11.390
to the pain of losing a loved one.

39:11.670 --> 39:13.400
My professor once told me this.

39:16.110 --> 39:18.040
Those who take their own lives are,

39:18.230 --> 39:19.830
in a way, placing their bones

39:20.550 --> 39:22.360
upon the hearts of the living.

39:24.070 --> 39:25.230
And that guilt,

39:25.960 --> 39:26.690
self-blame,

39:27.360 --> 39:28.160
and confusion

39:29.670 --> 39:30.840
weigh heavily on your heart

39:30.840 --> 39:33.300
for a long time
until you can barely breathe.

39:34.550 --> 39:35.610
That's true for you

39:36.630 --> 39:37.760
and for Jiale too.

39:42.510 --> 39:44.230
Set everything else aside for now.

39:44.230 --> 39:45.830
Focus on his feelings first.

39:46.920 --> 39:48.380
Before, there was Leilei.

39:49.070 --> 39:50.920
Now Jiale only has you.

40:07.490 --> 40:08.280
Don't fight.

40:10.150 --> 40:10.710
Let's go.

40:11.730 --> 40:12.930
-Bye-bye!
-Bye-bye.

40:16.510 --> 40:17.770
Be careful on the road!

40:30.590 --> 40:31.510
I'm sorry.

40:34.810 --> 40:37.780
Mom, I shouldn't have taken
Sun Haoyang's turtle.

40:40.600 --> 40:42.600
I'll give it back to him tomorrow.

40:45.760 --> 40:48.560
Actually, I did it not
just because I was mad at him.

40:48.960 --> 40:51.220
It's mainly because I saw him keep poking

40:51.230 --> 40:52.070
the turtle with his pencil

40:52.070 --> 40:53.670
and even jabbing at its eyes.

40:59.360 --> 41:00.320
Then we...

41:02.410 --> 41:03.810
won't give it back to him.

41:15.260 --> 41:17.300
Can we really set it free?

41:18.240 --> 41:20.300
Nothing is more important than life.

41:30.590 --> 41:31.110
Go on.

41:32.000 --> 41:34.010
Go find your friends.

41:39.710 --> 41:40.670
Thank you, Mom.

41:42.820 --> 41:45.440
I wish Godmother could release

41:45.440 --> 41:46.500
the turtle with us.

41:49.840 --> 41:54.480
[The Dark Romance]

41:56.960 --> 41:57.510
This way.

42:14.620 --> 42:20.490
[Yan Ling]

42:27.960 --> 42:28.910
See?

42:30.440 --> 42:31.690
Patience is key.

42:32.400 --> 42:33.200
Right?

42:40.550 --> 42:42.480
I'll be counting on you from now on.

42:49.940 --> 42:56.140
[Thanks, Dr. Luo.
My son and I are okay now.]
